des: The Tide Risers Alexa Skill is a companion tool for members of Tide Risers, a community for women leaders working toward the greater good. This Alexa Skill is designed to deepen and extend your Tide Risers experience with on-demand meditations, journaling prompts, and challenges designed to build community amongst our members, broaden your horizons, and lift you up and out of whatever loop may be holding you in place.
